list.name: Default
list.comment:
Added stub files from Google's example SyncAdapter. Changed initial activity to GoogleLoginActivity and set it to go to mainScreen on login. Extracted some of the GoogleApiClient code to a BaseActivity class so we don't have to reimplement some of this stuff in every activity. The login page is a special case for some of the methods, so it still has the BaseActivity methods @overriden.
Not sure if we're planning on keeping the original Login activity, but I swapped it out because it's a bit faster to test this way, and the Login activity seems redundant atm.
